    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To Clean The Mountain is a platforming adventure where you throw yourself towards the summit.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138520/extras/e9c3a4228417746e8c2149763fa7b0b0.poster.avif?t=1768703344\" width=920 height=666 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138520/extras/e9c3a4228417746e8c2149763fa7b0b0.webm?t=1768703344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138520/extras/e9c3a4228417746e8c2149763fa7b0b0.mp4?t=1768703344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Environments</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handcrafted levels based on a variety of mountainous landscapes. Each environment features unique mechanics for you to interact with and learn, combining the interesting platforming elements with puzzle solving. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138520/extras/5bffb79e04bee27564d990869eafcb96.poster.avif?t=1768703344\" width=1170 height=728 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138520/extras/5bffb79e04bee27564d990869eafcb96.webm?t=1768703344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138520/extras/5bffb79e04bee27564d990869eafcb96.mp4?t=1768703344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Mountain </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elements of the world change based on how you traverse the mountain. The game is completable regardless of your choices, but the difficulty is up to you.</p>",
